{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji28.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给周容的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给周容的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1950年5月16日）赞襄先生："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年八月惠书敬悉，甚感盛意，迟复为歉。组织问题，未便率尔绍介，应就当地有所表现，向当地组织请求，听候解决。此复，即祝进步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五○年五月十六日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]周容，又名周赞襄，1920年在湖南省立第一师范学校与毛泽东相识。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[2]指周容请求毛泽东介绍他加入中国共产党一事。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":5,"day":16}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":402,"page_end":402},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}